Sentiasa ingat, selepas kita ditangkap polis:
1. Kita ada hak utk buat satu phone call utk hubungi peguam
2. Jangan bercakap dgn polis tanpa ditemani peguam 
3. Masa perbicaraan reman, jangan menghadap magistret tanpa diwakili peguam
4. Call YBGK utk dapatkan khidmat peguam FOC
Translated Text:
Always remember, after we get caught by the police:
1. We have the right to make a phone call to contact a lawyer
2. Do not talk to the police without a lawyer
3. During the remand hearing, do not appear before the magistrate without being represented by a lawyer
4. Call YBGK to get the services of a FOC lawyer

Text: 1. Pastikan kamu tahu nama model & serial number modem & router kamu. Ambil gambar je sebab belah belakang ada info ni. Ini gambar modem aku yg dirampas. Walaupun aku langgan Maxis Broadband, modem tetap dari TM. Your TM modem punya serial number is linked to your name & account. https://t.co/hSrioVh7JQ
Translated Text: 1. Make sure you know the model name & modem serial number & your router. Just take a picture because there's this info on the back. This is a picture of my stolen modem. Even though I subscribe to Maxis Broadband, the modem is still from TM. Your TM modem has a serial number is linked to your name & accounts. https://t.co/hSrioVh7JQ

Text: 2. Selepas polis rampas modem & router kamu, pastikan mereka masukkan modem & router kamu dalam "Borang Senarai Pemeriksaan". Pastikan mereka tulis sekali nama model & serial number modem & router kamu dalam borang. Minta satu salinan fotokopi borang rampasan tu daripada polis.
Translated Text: 2. After the police seized the modem & your router, make sure they insert the modem & your router in the "Checklist Form". Make sure they write the model name & modem serial number & your router in the form. Ask for a photocopy of the seizure form from the police.

Text: 3. Selepas kamu dibebaskan dari lokap, pergi buat satu laporan polis yg kata modem & router kamu telah dirampas polis dan tujuan kamu buat laporan polis adalah untuk rujukan pada pihak TM/Maxis. Include the model & serial number dalam report. Dapatkan satu salinan repot polis.
Translated Text: 3. After you are released from the lockup, go make a police report that says modem & Your router has been seized by the police and the purpose of your filing a police report is for reference by TM/Maxis. Include the model & serial number in the report. Get a copy of the police report.

Text:
4. Hubungi TM/Maxis utk beritahu modem & router kamu dah kena rampas & kamu nak request mereka ganti yg baru. Mereka akan minta kamu email mereka bukti. Hantar salinan borang rampasan & repot polis tadi.

5. TM/Maxis akan hantar technician utk ganti modem & router kamu for free. https://t.co/GbPM5evrDi
Translated Text:
4. Contact TM/Maxis to tell the modem & Your router has been confiscated & you want to request them to replace the new one. They will ask you to email them proof. Send a copy of the seizure form & trouble the police earlier.

5. TM/Maxis will send a technician to replace the modem & your router for free. https://t.co/GbPM5evrDi

Text: Jawab soalan pasal butir-butir peribadi (nama, IC, alamat, pekerjaan, pendidikan) dan soalan yg kamu rasa selamat utk dijawab, tapi tolak utk jawab semua soalan lain yg kaitkan diri kamu dengan kes yg disiasat polis. Kamu ada hak utk berdiam diri dan tidak kantoikan diri kamu.
Translated Text: Answer questions about personal details (name, IC, address, occupation, education) and questions that you feel safe to answer, but refuse to answer all other questions that relate yourself to the case investigated by the police. You have the right to remain silent and not expose yourself.

Text: Aku dah banyak kali kena soalsiasat polis, tahun ni saja dah 5 kali. Setakat ni aku tak pernah lagi kena belasah polis bila aku jawab macam ni. Kalau polis pukul kamu, kamu boleh laporkan pada Jabatan Integriti & Pematuhan Standard (JIPS) Bukit Aman dan saman polis di mahkamah.
Translated Text: I have been questioned by the police many times, 5 times this year alone. So far I have never been beaten up by the police when I answer like this. If the police beat you, you can report to the Department of Integrity & Bukit Aman Compliance Standard (JIPS) and police suit in court.

Text:
Jika kamu disoalsiasat polis tanpa kehadiran peguam, kamu jawab:

"Sebelum saya jawab soalan tuan, benarkan saya utk call peguam saya dulu & minta dia hadir masa saya disoalsiasat"

Call Yayasan Bantuan Guaman Kebangsaan (YBGK) utk dapatkan free legal aid.
https://t.co/XrTvWxtvsr
Translated Text:
If you are questioned by the police without a lawyer present, you answer:

"Before I answer your question, allow me to call my lawyer first & ask him to be present when I am interrogated"

Call the National Legal Aid Foundation (YBGK) to get free legal aid.
https://t.co/XrTvWxtvsr

Text:
Bila kamu ditangkap polis kamu ada hak utk buat satu phone call. Telefon peguam kamu atau YBGK utk dapatkan free legal aid. Kamu ada hak utk berunding dgn peguam sebelum kamu jawab setiap soalan polis.

"Sebelum saya jawab soalan ni benarkan saya consult dengan peguam saya dulu"
Translated Text:
When you are arrested by the police you have the right to make a phone call. Call your lawyer or YBGK to get free legal aid. You have the right to consult with a lawyer before you answer any police question.

"Before I answer this question, allow me to consult with my lawyer first"

Text: @n_izzah Di dalamnya, terdapat dzikir Li Khomsatun yang diajarkan oleh KH Hasyim Asyari kepada murid-muridnya secara turun temurun. Dzikir ini berasal dari pendiri tarekat Syadiliiah yakni Imam Abu Hasan Asy-Syadzili.
Translated Text: @n_izzah In it, there is Li Khomsatun's remembrance which was taught by KH Hasyim Asyari to his students from generation to generation. This dhikr comes from the founder of the Syadiliiah order, namely Imam Abu Hasan Asy-Syadzili.

Text:
@n_izzah Dzikir ini juga terdapat dalam kitab Malahiq fi Fiqh Al Dakwah Al Nur, Karya Syaikh Badi’uzzaman Sa’id Al Nursi.

Keutaman dzikir Li Khomsatun ialah untuk menolak bala atau musibah yang salah satunya dapat berupa wabah.
Translated Text:
@n_izzah This dhikr is also found in the book Malahiq fi Fiqh Al Dakwah Al Nur, the work of Shaykh Badi'uzzaman Sa'id Al Nursi.

The priority of Li Khomsatun's dhikr is to ward off calamities or calamities, one of which could be the plague.

Text: @n_izzah Dzikir ini dimaksudkan agar seseorang dapat memperkuat iman dan keteguhan beragamanya ketika ditimpa musibah.
Translated Text: @n_izzah This dhikr is intended so that a person can strengthen his faith and religious firmness when disaster strikes.

Text:
@n_izzah Li Khomsatun maksudnya.
Saya mempunyai lima orang yang bisa menolak bala’, yaitu yang pertama, al-Musthafa (Nabi Muhammad SAW), yang kedua al-Murtadha (Ali bin Abi Tholib), dan kedua anaknya (Imam Hasan dan Imam Husain), serta yang kelima bernama Fathimah (putri Nabi Muhammad).”
Translated Text:
@n_izzah Li Khomsatun means.
I have five people who can resist the plague, namely the first, al-Musthafa (Prophet Muhammad SAW), the second al-Murtadha (Ali bin Abi Tholib), and his two sons (Imam Hasan and Imam Husain), and the fifth named Fatimah (daughter of the Prophet Muhammad)."
